product_brands.name: GHD
product_brands.content1: We are a big fan of GHD products in our as they help us to create spectacularly stunning hair styles and leave hair looking stylishly healthy. With GHD hair styling essentials, you will be able to create salon finish hairstyles every time.
product_brands.content2:
The GHD products use patented tri-zone technology, which maintains a safer-for-hair heat from root to tip, reducing hair breakage and increasing shine. Jennifer Aniston, Victoria Beckham, Madonna and countless more gorgeous women across the globe rely on the GHD product range every day, it is time for you to be also Guilty of a Good Day Hair!

Join the hairstyling revolution and discover GHD essentials such as GHD Air® Professional Hair Drying Kit - super fast hair drying tool with advanced ionic technology that will leave your hair silky, beautiful and frizz-free! Create beautiful classic waves with GHD Classic Wave Wandor poker-straight-hair with GHD Gold Classic Styler .

Don't forget to protect your locks from heat with GHD Heat Protect Spray and lock your creations with super strong GHD Final Fix Spray.

product_brands.name: Kerastase
product_brands.content1: Kérastase is a global leader in the luxurious hair care treatments. Kérastase products are scientifically developed to provide the most innovative hair care solutions on the market.
product_brands.content2:
Kérastase's Parisian scientific research centre constantly creates hair care product ranges which uniquely target individual hair care concerns. Kérastase exclusive products contain a distinct formula which combines potent active ingredients and molecular complexes that will restore hair strength, health, and shine.

We are big advocates of Kérastase products at our Beauty & Melody Salons as we know that they provide highly effective results and will give your hair luxurious and sophisticated care.

You can count on Kérastase with any hair concern and to treat yourself to a salon experience all year round, from the comfort of your own home. If you are fighting with hair loss try Kerastase Bain Chronologiste which will leave your hair very strong, eliminating any hair loss. Are you suffering from sensitive scalp? Try Kerastase Masque Dermo-Calm for a soothing effect along with a very soft hair texture.

product_brands.name: CACI
product_brands.content1: The world's leading beauty salons and spas have relied on non-invasive aesthetic treatments designed by CACI for years.
product_brands.content2:
CACI is an industry leader in non-surgical skin care, and has been for over two decades. It is also the largest British manufacturer of non-surgical beauty treatments. CACI's innovative products and technological breakthroughs deliver highly effective results, helping you look gorgeously young. Forget surgery or invasive procedures, with CACI treatments you can achieve dramatic results of younger looking skin in just a few weeks.

Thousands of people are already benefitting from impressive CACI results, including celebrities such as Jennifer Lopez, Michelle Collins, Lisa Snowdon, Barbara Windsor...

It is time to discover innovative skin care solutions by CACI and create your own luxury beauty salon in the comfort of your home.

We highly recommend powerful anti-ageing treatment CACI Amino-Lift Peptide Complex to help you diminish fine lines, wrinkles, age spots and acne scarring. If you are struggling to calm and refresh tired and puffy eyes try CACI Eue Revive Serum and CACI Hydro Eye Mask.

product_brands.name: LPG
product_brands.content1: LPG skincare provides innovative solutions, scientifically developed to optimise the natural cellular activity of your body. LPG patented technologies preserve anti-aging functions, leaving your skin beautiful and younger looking.
product_brands.content2:
LPG firming treatments are used in beauty salons across the globe to protect skin from ageing, hollowing, and thickening. LPG innovative formulas respect the skin and are the perfect substitute to potentially harming surgical solutions.

At Beauty & Melody Salons we are fascinated by LPG groundbreaking anti-aging solutions which are designed in natural and responsible way to preserve young, beautiful, and healthy looking skin.

Discover & refine your skin texture with LPG Anti-Ageing Renewal Serum enriched with micro pearls which smooth wrinkles, provide comfort and hydration. To restore your eyes contour try LPG Total Eye Care which will help you to reduce the appearance of dark circles, eliminate puffiness and smooth fine lines and wrinkles.

product_brands.name: Moroccan Oil
product_brands.content1: Moroccanoil set out to create the proper canvas for all hair care and hairstyling.
product_brands.content2: Our signature product, moroccanoil treatment, is the perfect foundation for hair. Complete with both styling and conditioning benefits, this award-winning formula infused with argan oil creates long-lasting smoothness, increases manageability, speeds up blow-dry time and boosts shine.
